      <h2 class="section-title">Ask your Claw what to automate.<br>It already knows.</h2>
      <p class="agentify-subtitle">Your agent has weeks of structured work history. Just ask — it'll find the repetitive workflows you don't even notice anymore and build the automation for you. No other skill on ClawHub has the data to answer this question.</p>
