            <span class="time">Mon 9:02</span>
            <span><span class="app">GitHub</span> — check PR notifications on dashboard repo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="af-activity">
            <span class="time">Mon 9:04</span>
            <span><span class="app">GitHub</span> — read diff, copy reviewer comments</span>
          </div>
          <div class="af-activity">
            <span class="time">Mon 9:06</span>
            <span><span class="app">Notion</span> — paste comments into sprint standup notes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="af-activity">
            <span class="time">Mon 9:09</span>
            <span><span class="app">Slack</span> — post summary in #dev-updates</span>
            <span class="repeated">3× this week</span>
          </div>
        </div>
