          <span class="dim">I found a pattern:</span> every weekday morning you check GitHub PR notifications → copy review comments → paste into Notion standup notes → summarize in Slack #dev-updates. <span class="dim">Avg. time spent:</span> 12 minutes. <span class="dim">Detected on:</span> Mon, Wed, Thu.
        </div>
      </div>

